title: EYL #165 Tax Deductions, Marketing, & Keys to Business
itunes:title: EYL #165 Tax Deductions, Marketing, & Keys to Business
description:
For episode 165, we returned to the essence of our foundation. No guests, just us discussing topics and providing information. We covered our plan to save over $200,000 in taxes this year, marketing, a little known tax loophole that can be extremely beneficial for business owners, we made a return to the story time segment, and we discussed our plans to expand our clothing brand. #taxes #marketing #business
